snippet.textDisplay: "Milon hobe kotodine, amar moner manushero shone" in simple bengali Means "When will I meet the person of my heart(desire the most) ". It might seem like another romantic song. But if you look deeper to other parts of the lyric, it'll become evident that Lalon Shaiji is talking about the inner being. He wants to meet his inner self, maybe it is god himself. Or maybe the god is who you see in the mirror. Either way it is fascinating to understand the words of this philosopher. Joy guru
